{"title":"大地回春（二首）","authors":["田牧"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":2,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地回春（二首）\t　　田牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报春花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫漫白雪的冬天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用满头柔细的绿发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精心编织着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一首美好的诗梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们惊喜地发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那绿色的朦胧里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆出了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点点蹦跳的金星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发表于一个季节的黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤醒沉睡的大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打动坚冰感化冷雪的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那首鲜绿的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——诗的眼睛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把过去一年的辛劳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拌在槽头的草料里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于雪花飘落的节奏中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反刍了整整一个冬季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从山岩般的背脊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到毛梢油亮的尾部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都贮满了鲜活的血液"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都积蓄了足够的气力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初春的曙色中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你张大鼻孔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽情地呼吸复苏的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那格外清新的气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁是硬弓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铧是利箭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用千钧之力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绷紧全身的肌肉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈开稳健的四蹄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉紧呼呼春风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拽亮阳光万缕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头，倔强地向前低垂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两只犀利的角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直指远方，奔突而去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在辽阔的大野上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你放射出一道道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力与韧性的深深轨迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻开，一个播种金色希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生长花香鸟鸣的新世纪！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}